Follow `AGENTS.md` and `docs/ai/STYLESEED-INTEGRATION.md`.

For UI work in this repo:
- Read `DESIGN.md` and `apps/web/src/styles.css` before making changes.
- Use StyleSeed from `docs/ai/styleseed/` as a judgment layer only.
- Keep the existing Beauté Avenue palette, typography, utilities, and Vue 3 + Tailwind 4 architecture.
- Reuse existing utility classes such as `page-title`, `entity-title`, `section-label`, `row-primary`, `row-meta`, `metric-value`, `metric-label`, `panel-clean`, `btn-primary`, `btn-secondary`, `btn-gold`, and `input-shell`.
- Use Heroicons only.
- Prefer improving existing screens over introducing a parallel component system.
